\(f\) has points of inflection at \(x = \)\{ans_rule(30)\}
$PAR
(ix) For which numbers \(c\) is the line \(y = c\) a horizontal asymptote for \(f\)? $BR
\(f\) has horizontal asymptotes for \(c = \)\{ans_rule(30)\}
